parameters:
Explorer Armada: Another dead end... It seems like there
might be some kind of mystery here too, huh?

Explorer Armada: But it's so beautiful... I can't believe
humans could have created such a space.

Mage Relm: I think it's safe to say that this is the
remains of a demon civilization!
Thief Nora: Look, there's something drawn on the floor!
Clea: Could this be a hint to unravel this place?

Explorer Armada: The shape of a triangle... Could it
be...!

Explorer Armada: As I thought...! There's a perfectly
fitting hole for this accessory!

Priestess Sophia: I see, so there are a total of four
marks. It seems that collecting all the keys will open the
door, is that how it works?

Explorer Armada: Well then, let's try it out right
away...!

Mage Relm: Wait a moment! If this is truly a demon ruins,
there might be traps.

Mage Relm: It would be better to prepare before
proceeding!

Explorer Armada: That's right, let's calm down a bit. Let
me know when you're ready to proceed.
Clea: I'm ready, please take care of me.

Explorer Armada: M-My body... everyone, run! Something
is... coming out of the floor... Ahhh!

Clea: We can't just leave it like that! I'll help you right
now, so please hold on!
Explorer Armada: I-I'm fine... but this...!

Explorer Armada: So, does this mean we made it through
here? Hahaha, ahahaha, ahahahaha!
Mage Relm: A-Are you okay? Is it the influence of magic!?

Explorer Armada: I can't help but laugh! How much closer
did we get to my dream today!

Explorer Armada: Thanks to everyone, if there's anything I
can do to help, please let me know.

Explorer Armada: I will definitely become everyone's
strength!
Clea: Yes, please count on me at that time.

Explorer Armada: There should be accessories that
correspond to the marks on the floor. I'll search through
the literature and investigate...!

Explorer Armada: Let's call it a day here for today. If the
investigation progresses, I'll submit a request. Please
count on me!

Explorer Armada: Phoni, thank you too. I might ask for your
help again, so please count on me!

Voice Priestess Phoni: Yes, if there's anything I can do,
I'll help as a way to repay Clea and the others.
Clea: Thank you for your assistance in slaying the dragon.

Explorer Armada: It's fine, we scratch each other's backs.
But more importantly, is Clea okay?
Clea: I can see what I can do now.

Explorer Armada: I see... It's good that you were able to
meet such good companions.

Explorer Armada: I appreciate you coming all this way.
Today, there has been progress in the investigation of the
ruins.

Explorer Armada: Let me explain what I found in the
documents.

Mage Relm: I see, so it's related to the demon of
regeneration, Jien, huh?

Explorer Armada: Originally, they were a group based in the
Kanonas region, but it seems they eventually fled to the
Bariere region.
Thief Nora: What were you running away from?

Explorer Armada: There are so many documents about the
hero, but it's highly likely that these were created in a
later era as fiction.

Explorer Armada: I found a place that seems to be related
to this star mark...

Priestess Sophia: There is a possibility that there are
accessories there as well.

Explorer Armada: It seems that the place they referred to
in their language was called 'Forma'.

Explorer Armada: First, let's go to the Seat of Sol. There
should be some hints there!
Explorer Armada: I'm excited to see what awaits us!
\CL Area Liberation\c[18]\CL Kanonas Region/Seat of Sol\c[0]
Adventurer Armada: I'm excited to see what awaits us!

Adventurer Armada: I'm glad you came. First, would you like
to have a star-shaped accessory?

Adventurer Armada: I believe that when you insert the same
accessory as last time, it should trigger a battle.
Clea: Shall we change the process of inserting it?

Adventurer Armada: I'll leave this to you. It's
frustrating, but I can't handle the monsters myself.
Adventurer Armada: Let me know when you're ready.
Clea: No problem, please take care of me.
Explorer Armada: Got it... Let's go!

Explorer Armada: Ugh... Gugaa! It's the same as last time,
the rest is up to you...!
Clea: Yes, I've been entrusted with it!

Explorer Armada: You did it... Thank you, I feel like I can
move my body now.

Explorer Armada: With this, it's halfway...! I really can't
thank everyone enough.

Explorer Armada: I'm currently investigating the location
of the next ruins. Once I decipher the documents, I'll
contact you again.
Clea: Yes, please take care of me.
Explorer Armada: That's right, the promised reward.

Explorer Armada: Next time, I'll request it through the
Varie bulletin board.

events.name: 貴族オリクトからの提案_不滅の真円アルマダ

parameters:
Explorer Armada: Honestly, I give up. Even if I search this
room again, I won't find anything.
Clea: Do you think this book will be useful?

Explorer Armada: This is quite an old book. Let me take a
look inside. Hmm...

Explorer Armada: Where did you get this? Did the little
mage from the Magic Academy find it!?

Mage Relm: N-No, that's not it! And please stop calling me
a little kid--

Clea: I received a request from Noble Orikuto to deliver
this book to Armada at the guild.

Explorer Armada: That guy... always causing trouble...!
Sorry, but I can't accept this.

Priestess Sophia: Why do you dislike it so much? Is it
because you have reservations about atonement for sins?

Explorer Armada: Sigh... So you've been talking about it
that much... He's just getting carried away on his own.

Explorer Armada: He and I are childhood friends, so he was
like an older brother to me.

Explorer Armada: The daughter of a miner and the son of a
noble, both of our dreams were to become archaeologists.

Thief Nora: If that's the case, then even more so... um...
it would be better if our relationship doesn't worsen,
right?

Explorer Armada: As I mentioned before, I seek romance,
while he seeks honor.

Mage Relm: It's fine to have honor as a goal, isn't it? As
someone from the academy, I can understand that.

Explorer Armada: That's not it... I can't explain it well,
but... I feel like the honor he seeks isn't just about the
ruins themselves.
Explorer Armada: Well, it's just women's intuition.
Clea: Is it okay if I throw away this book?
Explorer Armada: Huh, wait a minute!

Clea: If you won't accept it, then it's something
unnecessary for us, so I'll dispose of it.

Priestess Sophia: It's unfortunate, but there's nothing we
can do. Ah, I wanted to go to the final ruins.

Mage Relm: That's really unfortunate! To think that there
are ruins that won't be discovered by someone like me!

Explorer Armada: Ah, I understand, I understand! I really
want that book! It has a clue!
Explorer Armada: Hey, hand it over to me!
Clea: Here you go, I'll hand it over again.

Explorer Armada: This is why I'm not good with adventurers
from the guild!
Clea: I'll take that as a compliment.

Explorer Armada: We've come this far! I'll definitely make
sure you stick with us until the end!

Explorer Armada: We've come this far! I'll definitely make
sure you stay with me until the end!

Adventurer Armada: Finally, can I entrust you with the last
accessory?

Adventurer Armada: Once this is inserted, all preparations
will be complete... It's nerve-wracking, isn't it?

Adventurer Armada: I'll follow the usual procedure, but
sorry, I'll leave the fighting to everyone else.

Clea: Leave it to me. Let's solve the mystery of this room
together.

Clea: There's no problem. I'll release it soon, so please
wait.
Voice Priestess Phoni: I will also provide support!
Adventurer Armada: Ah, please rely on me... Let's go!

Adventurer Armada: That's strange... I don't feel the same
pain as before.

Clea: Please don't let your guard down. We still don't know
what might happen.

Adventurer Armada: Indeed... We don't know what might
happen.

Adventurer Armada: This sensation... It's the same as
before!

Adventurer Armada: It seems to have gone well... I'm glad
that nothing broke in the end.
Clea: Why aren't any enemies appearing?

Adventurer Armada: It's just a guess, but... Maybe they
were cornered to the point where they couldn't set up any
monsters.

Adventurer Armada: Well, the problem starts here... What
will happen? What will you show us!?

Clea: I will prepare for battle. We really don't know what
might happen.

Adventurer Armada: Ah, please rely on me... We need to stay
on guard--
Adventurer Armada: This... means we should proceed, right?
Clea: There is probably something special ahead.

Adventurer Armada: Actually, I really want to raise my
hands and celebrate, but I'll hold back until I see what's
ahead of the magic circle.

Adventurer Armada: Clea, is it possible to make a request
here? I want you to come with me all the way ahead, the
details of the request.
Clea: Understood. I will accept that request.

Adventurer Armada: I almost forgot, I want you to receive
the reward for this expedition.

Adventurer Armada: Thank you so much... Let me know when
you're ready.

events.name: 貴族オリクトからの依頼並列実行

parameters:
Explorer Armada: I'm glad you came! I found a new place, so
I want you to come with me!

Mage Relm: Where are we going next? I don't want any more
trouble like before!

Explorer Armada: Ahaha, there's no helping the commotion.
This time, I've called for reinforcements, so rest assured!
Clea: Are you calling for reinforcements?

Voice Priestess Phoni: Clea-san! I'm glad we can go on an
adventure together again!

Explorer Armada: Surprised, aren't you? I've asked for your
cooperation in investigating the ruins.

Priestess Sophia: You got permission quite easily, didn't
you?

Voice Priestess Phoni: Father said to grow through
interaction with Clea-san and the others...

Voice Priestess Phoni: Thanks to Clea-san and the others! I
will do my best, so please take care of me!
Clea: Yes, I'm counting on you.

Explorer Armada: If I'm not mistaken, Phoni, could it
be...?

Priestess Sophia: Hehe, sometimes silence speaks louder
than words.

Explorer Armada: The place I want to request an
investigation for is related to this square.
Thief Nora: What kind of place is it?

Explorer Armada: It seems to be believed that this was the
first base they used after being driven out of the Kanonas
region.

Explorer Armada: The place is a hill full of holes, indeed
a perfect place to hide.
Clea: Alright, let's head towards the hill full of holes.

\CL Area Liberation\c[18]\CL Valley Region/Hill Full of
Holes\c[0]

Explorer Armada: Thank you for coming and for protecting
the accessories. I appreciate it.

Clea: You mentioned that they were stolen. Do you have any
idea who might be responsible?

Explorer Armada: Ahaha, they call me the valiant woman of
Valier. I've earned quite a few grudges, you know.

Explorer Armada: Well then, I hate to ask, but I'll leave
the fighting to everyone while I focus on fitting the
accessories.
Explorer Armada: Let me know when you're ready.

Clea: I'm ready anytime. I'll defeat the monsters right
away.
Voice Priestess Phoni: I'll provide support too!
Explorer Armada: You're really reliable... Now, let's go!

Explorer Armada: Ugh, gahhh...! This, th-this is, I'm
counting on you...!
Clea: I've been entrusted with this! Here I go!

Explorer Armada: I-I guess it went well this time too.
Honestly, I'm not used to this feeling.

Explorer Armada: It's the same as last time... Take a
look!

Clea: With this, there's only one left. Which place should
we go to next?
Explorer Armada: Can you give me a little time?

Mage Relm: What have you come this far for? I also want to
witness it as a researcher!

Explorer Armada: I'm not trying to drag it out, but I can't
decide on the next location either.

Explorer Armada: The documents I obtained have many missing
parts, so I don't have any clues about the last location.

Explorer Armada: Ahaha, don't worry! I've gathered
materials over many years and achieved this much!

Explorer Armada: I'll find the last location! Make sure to
polish your skills by then.
Clea: Understood. I'll be waiting for your request.
Explorer Armada: That's right, it's the promised reward.

Explorer Armada: Thank you, Phoni. If it's alright with
you, please come with us next time too.

Voice Priestess Phoni: Yes, I will definitely cooperate
with you.

Explorer Armada: If there are any clues... I'll have to re-
investigate the literature one by one.

events.name: 強く儚いものたちアルマダ

parameters: Adventurer Armada: Are you ready? I'm always prepared.

Adventurer Armada: It might be a little early, but thank
you so much for helping me this far.

Adventurer Armada: I'm glad we made it this far, but more
than that... I'm grateful that you believed in this foolish
dream with me.
Adventurer Armada: I'm really happy, you know.

Mage Relm: There's no need for thanks! Everything we saw
was worth paying for, even if it meant spending money.

Thief Nora: Me too! It's fun to see so many amazing
things!

Priestess Sophia: Hehe, I'm the same. It's definitely an
adventure story that the children at the orphanage will be
delighted with.

Priestess Phoni: Me too! I'm really happy to be able to go
on an adventure with someone.

Clea: I've been called a fool, just like you. Let's go see
the end of what we believed in together.

Adventurer Armada: They're really good kids... Once
everything is settled, I'll definitely make sure to thank
them!

Adventurer Armada: Now, let's go...! To the end of this
magic circle... to the destination we have believed in.

強く儚いものたち1-7自動実行

parameters: Explorer Armada: That was a close call...

Clea: The thief-like man has disappeared, Nora-san. Do you
sense the presence of any allies?

Thief Nora: The scent remains, but I believe he probably
escaped together with someone.

Mage Relm: Sigh... We've come this far and still have no
results...

Priestess Sophia: I believe that the memories of an
exciting adventure alone are enough.

Explorer Armada: Actually, there are some results... \|...
\| Ect is not here.

Mage Relm: Could it be that you're planning to go back!?
There's a possibility that the magic circle has stopped
functioning!

Mage Relm: Please stop, Armada-san. There's a possibility
that you won't be able to return either!

Explorer Armada: Thanks... but you know, I have to repay
that guy's favor!
Voice Priestess Phoni: You won't come back, will you...

Thief Nora: Ugh... Relm-san, can't we do something about
this!?

Mage Relm: I'm desperately analyzing the magic circle right
now! What is this? Is the person who made it a genius or
something?!

Priestess Sophia: The magic circle... If it stays like
this, it's really...!
Clea: Wait... The magic circle is glowing--
Explorer Armada: Ahaha, looks like I made it just in time!

Explorer Armada: Ahaha, don't give me those scary looks.
I'll listen to your complaints later, so please spare me for
now.

Noble Ect: Why... did you save me...? Risking your own
life... why...

Explorer Armada: Did you forget? After the cave-in
accident, everyone gave up on searching for survivors.

Explorer Armada: But there was a man who continued to
search desperately on his own. Eventually, people were moved
by him and continued to follow.

Explorer Armada: Reach out your hand, I will definitely
rescue you. Your hand at that time was hotter and more
reliable than anything else.

Explorer Armada: Ahaha, with this, everything's settled!
That should be good enough, right, Brother Ect?

Noble Ect: No... I can't accept that! You've always been
pushing things forward without considering others!

Explorer Armada: You're always overthinking and self-
destructing on your own! You should be more carefree and
stop burdening yourself with everything, change your way of
living!

Priestess Sophia: Um, how long are we supposed to be
involved in this?

Noble Ect: ...Would you like to have a leisurely
conversation at my mansion, where I have been extremely rude
to all of you?

Explorer Armada: I don't mind, as long as there are no
hostages or violence.

Clea: Alright, please let me talk about the request I'm
receiving.

Explorer Armada: Yes, let's discuss that, including that
matter.
